---
import DonBosco from "../../../images/index/don-bosco.webp";
---

<div
  class="hero relative min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[600px] flex items-center px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12 py-10 md:py-8 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#e0f6f6] to-[#4fafb1]"
>
  <!-- Contenedor centrado -->
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Texto -->
    <div class="pl-0 md:pl-2 ml-1 text-center sm:text-left">
      <h1
        class="font-bold tracking-tight mb-2 md:mb-4"
      >
        <span
          class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2c9b9b] via-[#a1eaec] to-[#c0e6e6] bg-clip-text text-transparent text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.5rem] lg:text-[4rem] xl:text-[4.5rem] block leading-tight"
        >
          Un legado salesiano: <br />
          educación que transforma vidas
        </span>
      </h1>

      <div
        class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2c9b9b] via-[#a1eaec] to-[#c0e6e6] bg-clip-text text-transparent space-y-1 mt-6 md:mt-10"
      >
        <p>Formamos personas</p>
        <p>Íntegras y comprometidas.</p>
        <p>¿Listo para ser parte de nuestra misión?</p>

        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-block mt-8 bg-[#2c9b9b] hover:bg-[#136d6d] text-white text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 group"
        >
          Reserva tu vacante aquí
          <img
            src="/cursor.svg"
            alt=""
            class="inline-block w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 filter invert brightness-0"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Imagen Don Bosco -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 h-full lg:h-[90%] lg:w-[45%] flex items-start justify-end z-0 pointer-events-none pr-4 pt-6 md:pr-8"
  >
    <img
      src={DonBosco.src}
      alt="Don Bosco escribiendo"
      class="h-full max-h-[80vh] w-auto object-cover object-right md:object-contain rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3rem] opacity-70 md:opacity-100"
    />
  </div>
</div>
